319 inline bool CVarIndex::operator<(const CVarIndex& index) const
320 {
321  int count = m_elements.size();
322  int indexCount = index.m_elements.size();
323  int commonSize = qMin(count, indexCount);
324  for (int i = 0; i < commonSize; ++i){
325  int element = m_elements[i];
326  int indexElement = index.m_elements[i];
327  if (element != indexElement){
328  return element < indexElement;
329  }
330  }
331 
332  return count < indexCount;
333 }
